 * Date    : 03/28/2025  
 *
 * This script builds a dynamic configuration object for the Config Provider Node
 * based on the user's device type. It determines the appropriate delivery method
 * for identity verification for case of mobile or web browser and configures messaging and behavior accordingly.
 *
 * Script Inputs  : 
 *    - "forgeRock.device.profile" (Object) - Device metadata from node state
